<li><a href="http://www.rapidgrowthmedia.com/features/fennville32.aspx" class="external text" title="http://www.rapidgrowthmedia.com/features/fennville32.aspx" rel="nofollow">Fennville: A Haven for the Creative Class</a> - An article about the city of Fennville, Mich., which is an example of a city being transformed by the "creative class."</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ers.usda.gov/data/creativeclasscodes/" class="external text" title="http://www.ers.usda.gov/data/creativeclasscodes/" rel="nofollow">Creative Class Codes</a> - County-level measures of creative class from USDA's Economic Research Service.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.onmilwaukee.com/buzz/articles/florida.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.onmilwaukee.com/buzz/articles/florida.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a>- Florida Praises Milwaukee - onMilwaukee.com</li>
